title: 2021 Around the AFC in 48 Minutes
itunes:title: 2021 Around the AFC in 48 Minutes
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Patrick Claybon go around the AFC in 48 minutes starting with the Buffalo Bills (8:05). The heroes dive deep into Sessler's sleeping habits and also add a new rule change to the game. Timeouts incoming! Huge stop down for some major Teddy Bridgewater debate (53:17).
